{
  "texts": [
    "Give me each keyphrase separate by a \\n.",
    "Conceptually, these two prompts could be combined.",
    "However, we observed through experiments with GPT that directly asking for each keyphrase from the source document often produced only one keyphrase whereas more results were generated when asking for keyphrases within sentences selected for causality by GPT.",
    "In the example above, a sample answer could be [\"combination of lifestyle, exercise, diet and nutrition.",
    "\", \"economic factors\", \"cost of healthcare\", \"obesity\"]."
  ]
}